Some possible changes/enhancements for iceWing
----------------------------------------------

- Enhanced plugin info window:
    - Continous update
    - Graphical plugin graph
    - Possibility to display stored data elements
- Callbacks for all widgets
- Enhanced image rendering:
    - Support HSI/LUV/LAB
    - Render in the complete window, including right/bottom border.
- 3D-Support for rendering
- UTF-8 / freetype support for text rendering
- Enhanced preview windows:
    - Optional status bar with cursor info and zoom/pan buttons
    - Docking of multiple windows
    - Syncronized panning / multiple views on one window
    - Enhaced panning/zooming: Cursors
                               Zoom by marking a rectangle
- JPEG2000 load support
- Save as EPS
- Start/End image: Restrict image range for the "Image Num" slider
- Color selector widget
- Text widget
- GUI for the camera drivers for changing properties/pixel formats
- Allow all widgets/menu entries to be remote controllable (e.g. "Save Seq")
- Enhanced GTK 2.x support
- CMake-support for plugins?

- Docu enhancements:
  - Tips:
      mencoder mf://*.jpg -mf fps=25:type=jpg -ovc lavc -lavcopts vcodec=mpeg4 -oac copy -o video.mpg 
      transcode --use_rgb -x imlist,null -g 384x288 -i list -y divx4,null -o test.avi
      montage -depth 8 -geometry 384x288+0+0 i1.png i2.png o.png
